originalText.text: As an acupuncturist myself, I sought out Elizabeth Carpenter when my husband and I were having trouble conceiving because I knew she was a protege of Randine Lewis.  Elizabeth was instrumental to me becoming pregnant.  Because of her attention to detail and her gifts as an energy worker, she helped my physicians uncover a very deep imbalance that none of them could detect.  I required three surgeries to repair what was wrong and because of Elizabeth's work, I didn't waste time trying to conceive prior to the repair.  Elizabeth also directed me to an amazing doctor who figured out what I needed in order to bring my body back into a fertile state.  Elizabeth is capable of walking people through the life crisis of infertility because of her extensive experience, her ability to really see you as an individual and her extreme professionalism.  at this point, I wouldn't go to anyone else in NYC for Chinese herbs because all of her prescriptions were easy to digest and exacting in their purpose.   If you want to increase your chances of becoming pregnant and shorten the time it takes, I highly recommend investing in Ms. Carpenter's Fertility Program.  The fact that I conceived is a pure miracle and was an arduous and extensive journey.  I truly believe that Elizabeth made that journey as short and progressive as possible.  Thank you Elizabeth!

originalText.text: Anyone who has battled through fertility issues knows the long and sometimes painful road that we travel. Meeting Elizabeth changed my life.. I was on another path, shall we say the Western medicine conveyor belt and had recently been faced with several disappointments. I needed a fresh start, someone to actually pay close attention to the details of the process, take time in understanding my journey, and finally, to change its course. That person is Elizabeth! She is extremely knowledgeable, caring, considerate and is helping me achieve my goals in a thoughtful and well planned out approach that is actually good for you! Every time I leave her office I feel centered. I highly recommend her to anyone who wants to be at their best!!!! Her staff is also amazing, which is such a bonus!!

I had an excellent experience with Elizabeth.

I went to her with a trapped nerve in my shoulder. After the first session using the Bowen Technique I could raise my arm. My shoulder and hip dramatically improved in 3 sessions and I went from minimum to normal movement. Also helped my jaw too. Would highly recommend if you have any structural challenges that need dramatic results.
